## Limitations

The findings are based on a limited number of sources, which may not cover all perspectives on the topic. Additionally, the articles reviewed primarily focus on the benefits of student entrepreneurship, with less emphasis on potential drawbacks or challenges. Further research could explore these aspects to provide a more balanced view. Moreover, the rapidly changing educational and economic landscapes mean that some insights may become outdated quickly.